# AETHER RMX3171 — vendor_dlkm.modules.load
#
# Modules loaded after /vendor + /vendor_dlkm mount, during late init.
# Order matters; group by subsystem.
#
# Naming convention follows Samsung 6.6 MTK driver build artifacts.
# Mismatches with actual built .ko names get fixed iteratively after first
# `make modules` produces real filenames.

# ============================================================
# AETHER ported drivers (Phase 2+3+5)
# ============================================================
